{"tid":437120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拍緊拖嘅兄弟入一入","createTime":"2017-10-15T16:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T22:46:59.000Z","uid":147789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e885c368505efde841aabf149c0154eb4b3e2a8b","tid":437120,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"小弟拍咗年半 <br />\n女友會主張AA 又唔准我浪費錢買野比佢<br />\n特別節日直情可以唔洗用一大筆錢搞驚喜<br />\n真係好好<br />\n但係佢啲脾氣真係好難頂<br />\n就啱啱同佢skype <br />\n因為打風關係成日斷線  佢就已經燥底<br />\n之後我溫緊書  大概一至兩分鐘冇講野<br />\n佢問我做咩唔講野  我話溫緊書<br />\n佢話唔阻我 就cut咗我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係平時佢一路睇小說一路skype 唔講野<br />\n就話自己唔可以一心二用  當冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉<br />\n有冇人女友都係咁 成個人都好好 好啱傾<br />\n但係脾氣就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請教下你地會點教化女友 我想長久<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ad57c6f5cbb3ae2db0ea6c478af6bd09d6173c","tid":437120,"uid":98319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:49:29.000Z","msg":"佢要你同佢skype唔比你温書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174d61ad8b8004e30a101455e31b5dfaa3065bd0","tid":437120,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:50:58.000Z","msg":"溫緊書都要skype<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?叫佢咪撚咁阻釘啦"},{"pid":"0c98b3c96d31ddfa10bc2c3a305334ee2ef0548d","tid":437120,"uid":113583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:52:08.000Z","msg":"潤鳩我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358f2053a6452f8b845253d6181